---
title: Honey-Sesame Chicken Tenders with Crunchy Cabbage Slaw and Fragrant Jasmine Rice
description: A quick and simple soy, ginger, honey and sesame marinade gives these chicken tenders a sticky and sweet taste. The black sesame studded slaw adds a crunchy bite, while the fragrant  rice rounds out the dish.  All within 30 minutes!
